            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-10/51_0.jpg?VersionId=lWfidzY_Taq8dsk.mY4CWDjX7F2Ilva_&amp;itok=F-1PnB0n" title="上海市委书记李强星期一召开会议，强调要全力推动二十大精神在上海落地落实。（澎湃新闻）" alt="上海市委书记李强星期一召开会议，强调要全力推动二十大精神在上海落地落实。（澎湃新闻）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-10/51_0.jpg?VersionId=lWfidzY_Taq8dsk.mY4CWDjX7F2Ilva_&amp;itok=F-1PnB0n" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
